00263 enum PCConnState { // this is used exclusively inside ProcessInfo
00264 
00265     PC_STARTING,    // Waiting for Login confirmation
00266     PC_READY,       // Connection has been established. Nothing going
00267                     //   on.  Just waiting to be used.
00268     PC_EXECUTING,   // Very short phase between sending the command
00269                     //   and getting the starttoken
00270     PC_BUSY,        // Have received the starttoken, so all output is
00271                     //   sent to the "owner"
00272     PC_ENDING       // Have received the endtoken.  Now in doing term
00273                     //   sequence
00274 };
